			Total Stupid Comments : 7891
    		<h1>Stupid Client Quote #3109</h1><br />



			

			<br /><div id="RateForm" class="RateForm"><form name="rating" method="post" action="quotes.php?id=3109">Rate this Quote:
	    <select class="form-input" name="rating"> 
	    <option value="5.0" selected>5 - Excellent</option> 
	    <option value="4.0">4 - Good</option> 
	    <option value="3.0">3 - Fair</option> 
